01:18:55.744 --> 01:18:57.978
All right, all right, all right.

01:18:57.980 --> 01:19:00.413
Ben. Benjamin, I'm okay.

01:19:00.415 --> 01:19:01.614
Okay, all right.

01:19:01.616 --> 01:19:04.219
