<i>See you in the car, buddy.</i>

01:19:40.791 --> 01:19:43.592
- <i>Hiya!</i>
- <i>That's perfect.</i>

01:20:01.813 --> 01:20:03.445
<i>Luke, come on,</i>

01:20:03.447 --> 01:20:04.813
<i>you know you didn't have
to get me anything.</i>

