- <i>You did!</i>

01:20:07.350 --> 01:20:09.884
<i>Whatever could it be?</i>

01:20:09.886 --> 01:20:12.754
- <i>Well, you think it's a ball.</i>
- <i>I think maybe it's a ball, okay.</i>

01:20:12.756 --> 01:20:15.626
<i>All right, I'm gonna open it up.
Let me see here.</i>

01:20:16.359 --> 01:20:18.295
<i>Wow! It is...</i>

01:20:18.896 --> 01:20:20.395
<i>absolutely perfect.</i>

01:20:20.397 --> 01:20:22.297
<i>Everything I want.</i>

01:20:22.299 --> 01:20:24.399
<i>Thank you very much,
buddy.</i>

01:20:24.401 --> 01:20:25.768
- <i>That's...</i>
- <i>Dad, do you like it?</i>

01:20:25.770 --> 01:20:28.637
<i>I made it myself
so you can play too!</i>

01:20:28.639 --> 01:20:30.439
